race.comment: CLASSIC STORY (2) boasts a strong record this journey with four wins and four minors from 12 tries. Comes off a (29.50) win last time, scoring by 1.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 509m at Northam. Rates a leading player. IMPRESS HAWKINS (5) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 2.75 lengths (27.57) at this track. Expected to feature again. CHAROS GRAND (1) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 300m behind Fancy That Fred (17.58) in a Free For All. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. In the mix. BUTLER'S CABIN (8) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.
